Wonders of Ragay

  · rpetndsoSof91460r, ea6328hcr3821y0ua bgggg34m061t1gt9c16F302  ·
CORTEZ BEACH and FR. DAVE BEACH
Brgy. Upper Omon
Omon can be considered as the Summer Capital of Ragay. Why not? Its coastlines were blessed with beautiful beaches.
One of the most popular beach is located in Upper Omon, a stretch of long white sand combined with white pebbles and broken pieces of corals, the CORTEZ BEACH on the right and FR. DAVE on the left. Cottages are available at the rate of Php. 300.00 up. For those who love to sing, videoke is available at Fr. Dave Beach. Surely, you'll enjoy your summer with taking a dip in the crystal clear water with your love ones.
For more summer getaway ideas, please follow Baeyahero Diary for my nature trips outside Ragay. Thank you.
